data.title: Coxsackie, New York Population 2024
data.text:
Poverty in Coxsackie

The race most likely to be in poverty in Coxsackie is Other , with 85.23% below the poverty level.

The race least likely to be in poverty in Coxsackie is White , with 4.64% below the poverty level.

The poverty rate among those that worked full-time for the past 12 months was 2.23% . Among those working part-time, it was 11.67% , and for those that did not work, the poverty rate was 8.32% .
